{"componentChunkName":"component---node-modules-gatsby-theme-portfolio-minimal-src-templates-article-index-tsx","path":"/my-first-article/python/python6/","result":{"pageContext":{"article":{"banner":{"alt":"파이썬 기초","caption":"Photo by <u><a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/Nc5Q_CEcY44\">Google</a></u>","src":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/fe2007ff5fefc27a884eb9773510900b/b87af/pythonlogo.png","srcSet":"/static/fe2007ff5fefc27a884eb9773510900b/ea049/pythonlogo.png 125w,\n/static/fe2007ff5fefc27a884eb9773510900b/bf58b/pythonlogo.png 250w,\n/static/fe2007ff5fefc27a884eb9773510900b/b87af/pythonlogo.png 500w","sizes":"(min-width: 500px) 500px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/fe2007ff5fefc27a884eb9773510900b/df328/pythonlogo.webp 125w,\n/static/fe2007ff5fefc27a884eb9773510900b/2d2c6/pythonlogo.webp 250w,\n/static/fe2007ff5fefc27a884eb9773510900b/01f4a/pythonlogo.webp 500w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 500px) 500px, 100vw"}]},"width":660,"height":399.96}}}},"body":"<h2>불리언</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>불리언 또는 불(bool)이라고 하며, 참(True)과 거짓(Flase)을 나타내는 자료형이다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3>자료형별 데이터의 참/거짓</h3>\n<h4>숫자형</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a_int <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>\nb_int <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1.0</span>\nc_int <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1234</span>\nd_int <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.0</span>\n\n<span class=\"token builtin\">bool</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>a_int<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token builtin\">bool</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>b_int<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token builtin\">bool</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>c_int<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token builtin\">bool</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>d_int<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">(False, True, True, False)</code></pre></div>\n<h4>문자형</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a_str <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span>\nb_str <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"music\"</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin\">bool</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>a_str<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">bool</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>b_str<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">(False, True)</code></pre></div>\n<h4>리스트</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a_lst <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> \nb_lst <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">list</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># list() -> []</span>\nc_lst <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\nd_lst <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'a'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'b'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n\n<span class=\"token builtin\">bool</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>a_lst<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">bool</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>b_lst<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">bool</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>c_lst<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">bool</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>d_lst<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">(False, False, True, True)</code></pre></div>\n<h5>꼬일수 있는 경우?</h5>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">ab_lst <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># -> True 이지만</span>\nab_lst<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> ab_lst<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># -> 은 각각 False이다.</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 리스트에서는 값이 하나있는 경우에 ac_lst = [123] 이지만</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 튜플에서는 뒤에 콤마을 붙여주어야 한다. ax_lst = (123,)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">(0, '')</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>리스트에서는 값이 하나있는 경우에 ac_lst = [123] 이지만</li>\n<li>튜플에서는 뒤에 콤마을 붙여주어야 한다. ax_lst = (123,)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>튜플</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a_tup <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nb_tup <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">tuple</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nc_tup <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nd_tup <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token builtin\">bool</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>a_tup<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">bool</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>b_tup<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">bool</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>c_tup<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">bool</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>d_tup<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">(False, False, True, True)</code></pre></div>\n<h4>딕셔너리</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a_dic <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> \nb_dic <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">dict</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> \nc_dic <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token string\">'a'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token builtin\">bool</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>a_dic<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">bool</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>b_dic<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">bool</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>c_dic<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">(False, False, True)</code></pre></div>\n<h4>집합</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a_set <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">set</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> \nb_set <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">set</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nc_set <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">set</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'a'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'b'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token builtin\">bool</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>a_set<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">bool</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>b_set<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">bool</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>c_set<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">(False, True, True)</code></pre></div>","categories":["ALL","Python"],"date":"October 11, 2023","description":"파이썬 기초","id":"a4d5ff3a-cf36-5d5b-875c-59340af5085d","keywords":["Python","기초","불리언"],"slug":"/my-first-article/python/python6/","title":"[파이썬 기초] 불리언","readingTime":{"text":"2 min read"}},"listingPagePath":"/blog"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3262260831","948380417"],"slicesMap":{}}